{"tid":346243,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男朋友係咁用隻手係我額頭寫字","createTime":"2017-08-03T19:07:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T17:13:23.000Z","uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75a4fec3e60293176ae14b8ca31269c9617c5722","tid":346243,"uid":75115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:07:16.000Z","msg":"佢用隻手指係我額頭係咁寫字<br />\n寫左幾筆就係度笑 停下笑下又繼續寫<br />\n問佢笑乜鳩又唔講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n寫左幾次同一隻字 問佢寫咩又係度笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\no的情侶平時都係寫下我愛你啊乜乜乜&hellip;<br />\n佢奷笑左好耐 然後笑住咁問我<br />\n你有無試過比人係額頭寫個柒字？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無尊重過我？我係咪要同佢分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我最後緊係還拖啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/u53632IMG_20175402p29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fu53632IMG_20175402p29.jpg&h=440aec1e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0ce284f735624a58d0d7ffc285430d66f4a94a5e","tid":346243,"uid":17081,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:10:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/787/356/d6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.kym-cdn.com%2Fphotos%2Fimages%2Fnewsfeed%2F000%2F787%2F356%2Fd6f.jpg&h=bac9ecb7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"78080eae8f643ee22d3d879b01a01d955c9a68d9","tid":346243,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T19:12:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://i1.kym-cdn.com/photos/images/newsfeed/000/787/356/d6f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi1.k